% Exercise 1: Explore the Diversity in the Simplicity

Review a most simplified HTML5 page in various browsers and devices to get a feel for the baseline in a bunch of different places.

1. Load and view the first version of the [scene from *The Tempest*](tempest.html) in browsers that you have with you. Desktop, any devices. You can also find this web page hosted externally at <http://lyzadanger.com/d/101>.
2. Review screen shots of the same page rendered in various devices (below).
3. Try out the [Opera Mini simulator](http://www.opera.com/developer/tools/mini/) (load up the version at <http://lyzadanger.com/d/101>).

